Package: ssCTPR
Type: Package
Title: Cross-Trait Penalized Regression using Summary Statistics
Version: 1.2
Date: 2021-11-13
Author: Yingxi Yang <yingxi.yang@yale.edu>, Liming Liang <lliang@hsph.harvard.edu>
Maintainer: Yingxi Yang <yingxi.yang@yale.edu>
Description: A Polygenic Risk Score (PRS) method based on elastic net regression using 
      summary statistics from trait of interest and secondary trait(s) which are genetically 
      correlated with the primary trait.
